{"tid":919470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"審計報告發現，警務處行動裝備採購工作存在多項問題","createTime":"2018-11-28T05:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T06:05:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d952448a0aa1c72a3a7a9372bffb706f31a8aa11","tid":919470,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T05:19:01.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】審計報告發現，警務處行動裝備採購工作存在多項問題。<br />\n<br />\n警務處兩年前以6930萬元購入129架特別用途車輛，但承辦商延遲交付車輛，部分車輛在開始使用不久就出現毛病及有裂痕。截至今年9月，仍有5輛大型客貨車基於質量問題，被機電工程營運基金拒收。審計報告建議警務處加強特別用途車輛的實地驗收測試。<br />\n<br />\n另外，審計報告審查警務處15至16年度及17至18年度共190宗採購，發現兩成半都涉及重複購買性質相同或類似的物品。雖然部分採購是為應付緊急運作需要，但審計署認為有需要整合採購，達至更佳經濟效益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=328842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328842&d=L7ldDF1pPEK493UQQPpdLgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6724edfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328842&h=5ed6a2d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=328842</a>"},{"pid":"c4b2386bc94e2c71536d5d540865beb6c658a79b","tid":919470,"uid":68133,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"阿SIR做嘢唔洗你教"},{"pid":"ee1a25fa360fc32209469fa8784fe3f9bf053a01","tid":919470,"uid":64582,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T05:20:31.000Z","msg":"講完就算, 又無權管, 9得閒理你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825abe97d1dc1e0c8d10ff1fd87558f7e37897ac","tid":919470,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"用黎訓覺 有冷氣OK 啦"},{"pid":"9ee75809cb293d2b997b3ae4c6194aa9e997f432","tid":919470,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T05:22:37.000Z","msg":"<em><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特別用途車輛</span></strong><